### AgroSmart AI - exemple REST (extensia REST Client)

@host = http://localhost:8000

### Healthcheck
GET {{host}}/health

### Login (demo)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=fermier&password=agrosmart2025

@token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Profil
GET {{host}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Trimite citire senzor
POST {{host}}/sensors/analiza
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lat": 46.77,
  "lon": 23.62,
  "ph": 6.5,
  "umiditate": 24.0,
  "temperatura": 28.0
}

### Listeaza ultimele 20 citiri
GET {{host}}/sensors/?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sumar analytics
GET {{host}}/analytics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
